{"tid":532621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保安涉以鑽殺女友案 目擊證人指打999及到警署報警均不獲理會","createTime":"2018-01-18T04:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T05:13:21.000Z","uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"95717ffdd0beae6f91ac8841adf91d6d53a9425f","tid":532621,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"巴籍保安員涉以電鑽殺女友案，今於高院續審，控方傳召被告友人兼報案人Khan作供。Khan供稱當日目睹被告與女友吸食冰毒後爭執並大打出手，他阻止不了，於是聯絡家人求助。家人將屯門警署的電話告訴他，但他致電後對方卻要求提供詳細地址；由於地盤沒有地址，故他直接前往屯門警署，但遭趕走，警員叫他打999；他依言打999，999電台卻叫他返回現場等候。最終他在現場附近截停警方衝鋒車並引領警員到現場。<br />\n<br />\nKhan供稱，認識被告15年，認識Bayr Andrea則數個月。他知道被告吸毒有5年，事發前數月被告開始越吸越多，以致影響神志，例如胡言亂語或自言自語。他又謂Bayr Andrea經常與被告見面並帶毒品給他，雖然曾見兩人爭執但未見過他們打架。而<span style=\"color: red;\">他記不起當晚自己有否與兩人一起吸毒，但否認毒品是他帶去的</span>。他又指被告曾向他表示深愛Bayr Andrea並想跟她結婚，但Khan承認，這只是被告單方面說法，女方沒向Khan提及過結婚的事。<br />\n<br />\n法醫沈昊翔則透露，死者右眼下方插有一枝全長15.5厘米的鑽嘴，其中8厘米插入頭內，深入至顎骨。另死者體內驗出含有毒品。辯方問驗屍能否得知死者生前曾生下四名孩子，法醫稱不知。<br />\n<br />\n沈昊翔指，死者頭部多處受創，腦部出血，與受硬物如電鑽機身撞擊脗合，頸部深層瘀傷及軟骨裂傷則與以手扼頸造成壓力引致的傷勢脗合，他指死者的頭及頸傷皆可導致死亡。<br />\n<br />\n保安Safdar Husnain(27歲)，被控於2016年3月29日在屯門天后路10號對出的地盤謀殺Bayr Andrea。<br />\n<br />\n聆訊明續，屆時將開始辯方案情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180117/57718864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F57718864&d=yRN%2Fokt7E13NHUuX5ep%2Fq8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d449ca61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F57718864&h=0cffae9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180117/57718864</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 電鑽殺人狂"},{"pid":"8fd7d31fae5be388cab9c76e196a286762b27561","tid":532621,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑荷屌你老母"},{"pid":"dab101b043438867e094d41f6c3de2343da1ae78","tid":532621,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8fd7d31fae5be388cab9c76e196a286762b27561","tid":532621,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑荷屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"警"},{"pid":"d9708a447ca95e3ff022ef29043980795d5e20c8","tid":532621,"uid":116131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"啲警犬係咪聽唔明英文所以唔落案？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n殺人咁大件事，打去差館無人理，親身行去警署又無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成件事咁on9"},{"pid":"b489af350fdad913186624d49387d4aa855ca6b7","tid":532621,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:36:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18c7380a5befd6f95ce343057c9171899d762085","tid":532621,"uid":86893,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/h4029814434_12f152.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fh4029814434_12f152.jpg&h=5f0ce8be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab13677faaab04c08361a9bf06e3f1ff48780b4d","tid":532621,"uid":72676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"咁大個人連打去999報警都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要打翻屋企先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716021a396e1129